# QA Checklists

## Structural QA
- `README.md` exists
- `HANDOFF.md` exists
- `00_admin/canon_lock.yaml` exists
- `00_admin/package_manifest.json` exists
- Required TV package files exist

## Canon QA
- Title, logline, format, and genre match canon
- Characters and episode list match canon
- Canon fingerprint is embedded in generated markdown frontmatter

## Editorial QA
- No `TODO`, `TBD`, or unresolved handlebars tags remain
- Public website pages only use approved public fields
- Press-facing summary matches current approved logline
